        <span class="inline-block bg-orange-500 px-6 py-2 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl transform rotate-1">Count</span>
        <span class="inline-block bg-yellow-400 text-purple-900 px-6 py-2 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl transform -rotate-1 ml-2">Cachula</span>
